msgid "3a. Composer Upgrade (recommended)"
msgstr "3a. Mise à niveau via Composer (recommandé)"

#: ../../admin/upgrading.rst:88
msgid ""
"If you had your Elgg 2.3 project installed using composer, you can follow "
"this sequence:"
msgstr ""
"Si vous aviez installé votre projet 2.3 avec composer, vous pouvez suivre la"
" séquence suivante :"

